on Mike, summer '77?

100
00:05:17,805 --> 00:05:19,324
I don't know that man.

101
00:05:19,324 --> 00:05:22,074
Seen this goat 
charm before, Roy?

102
00:05:22,074 --> 00:05:23,217
Not that I recall.

103
00:05:23,217 --> 00:05:25,041
Sure it didn't come 
from one of your victims.

104
00:05:25,041 --> 00:05:27,187
Cuz it was in the trunk 
with all your other trophies.

105
00:05:27,187 --> 00:05:29,103
- Was it?
- Yeah.

106
00:05:29,103 --> 00:05:32,412
And we think that you took it off of this 
kid after you made him your first kill.

107
00:05:32,412 --> 00:05:34,236
No, sir.

108
00:05:34,499 --> 00:05:36,666
Let's hear about 
your stay in Philly, Roy.

109
00:05:36,666 --> 00:05:38,325
From the beginning.

110
00:05:38,325 --> 00:05:42,709
Well, my father took me 
there when I was 21.

111
00:05:42,709 --> 00:05:44,001
Fresh from Provo.

112
00:05:44,001 --> 00:05:45,438
It must've been a shock.

113
00:05:45,438 --> 00:05:46,653
Big city and all.

114
00:05:46,653 --> 00:05:48,235
It was indeed, ma'am.

115
