to talk to her.

234
00:11:59,196 --> 00:12:00,916
I gotta see someone tomorrow.

235
00:12:00,916 --> 00:12:03,104
Day after?

236
00:12:03,104 --> 00:12:05,034
That should be good.

237
00:12:05,682 --> 00:12:07,559
It's gotta be.

238
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:10,387
Cuz I ain't leaving Philly without her.

239
00:12:29,385 --> 00:12:31,832
Hey, Scotty, 
Roy's aunt is here.

240
00:12:32,799 --> 00:12:34,624
Yeah, okay.

241
00:12:40,395 --> 00:12:43,786
What did this 
NY detective want?

242
00:12:44,379 --> 00:12:46,069
This girl I been with,

243
00:12:46,069 --> 00:12:50,283
he's saying she did
credit card fraud.

244
00:12:50,426 --> 00:12:52,813
Which is crazy.

245
00:12:53,995 --> 00:12:57,318
Does Lil know this guy's 
looking for her sister?

246
00:13:01,715 --> 00:13:03,935
Yeah.

247
